sentence: what is the state with the highest elevation in the united states ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the state with the highest elevation in the united states ?
sql: select highlow.state_name from highlow where highlow.highest_elevation = ( select max ( highlow.highest_elevation ) from highlow ) ;
